Installation
------------

Simple method (quadratic method)

>	make hcmd    

Fast method (linear method)

>	make fhcmd 


The fast version yields slightly different results from the simple one.
This should be checked again and fixed as soon as possible.


Utilization
-----------

>	hcmd > output_file_name



Making PostScript movies
------------------------

>	makemovie.p output_file_name


The result is saved in the video file "output_file_name.mp4" 





